[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/overcalls"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has a very minimum Takeout Double of 1\D. But what it lacks 
in strength, it makes up for with perfect distribution.

EAST has 13 points and only wants to play in one contract, 4\H.

WEST passes happily.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "W"]
[Vulnerable "None"]
[Deal "W:K52.A98.K52.J987 AT94.KQJ7.Q6.AQ4 Q83.643.T873.653 J76.T52.AJ94.KT2"]
